description: National Environmental Action Plan Support Programme

subproject.description: 1. Comprehensive analysis of existing situation of environmental information in Pakistan. 2. Datasets, indicators and indices for monitoring the state of the environment finalized in consultation with stakeholders. 3. Appropriate institutional and technical framework for NEIMS Pakistan is established. 4. Development of database relating to various sectors of environment and inter-sectoral existing database of environmental information in the country and their networking supported by GIS and remote sensing. 5. Build and strengthen the capacity of key organizations involved in establishment & operation of NEIMS.
subproject.title: (E&E)-NEIMS
